{
  "stem": "21812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- I went-- there was a temple called the Polish Temple across the street from our building, which was burned down during Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now there's a plaque in-- on the building that they elected there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish Temple.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called the Polish Temple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on Leopoldstrasse, right across the street from us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, we could watch the, the choir rehearse and-- because it was that close.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could look into that window where they rehearsed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but I was not bar mitvahed there That was a unorthodox one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was bar mitvahed within a conservative one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't recall the name now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A Very large synagogue in the-- near, near Praterstrasse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't remember the name of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in school, religion was a subject that was taught in school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So two or three times a week-- I forgot now, maybe twice a week-- we attended a class in religion.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I also attended, for about a couple of years, I attended, in addition, which was optional, in the afternoon, a Hebrew class, modern Hebrew class.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean general?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the religious topics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the religious topics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Bible, mostly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was taught in the, in the religious school, in the religious class.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I said, the optional taught modern Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- that, again, was done by that Hebrew teacher who taught us in school, and-- the religious teacher.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had to perform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, afterwards, we had a party in my apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in those days, you got books and fountain pens, mostly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] There were about 12 kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother did the cooking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And uncles and aunts came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the, the party.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
